description: Koagie Hots is a Korean influenced food truck serving cheesesteaks, hot dogs and much more.Our Koagie's begin with a fresh, daily-delivered french baguette loaded toppings such as in-house marinated Korean BBQ ribeye, our signature kimchi made by Chef Pak, onions, aioli, and the customers' option of provolone or wiz. Our unique spin on a “Korn Dog” and fries is definitely worth checking out as well. ​Come by and see us!
name: Koagie Hots
